Welcome To Sick Weather World

Each Files Optional Suffix .weather.br Contain The Weather Of The City Line By Second And One Day Duration, Generate By My Script, Compressed As ZStandard, Please Download All For Distribut
Load Your City Name My City.weather.zst, For Example Dubai.weather.zst File If You Living In Dubai
Type The Command To get Your Weather ::::::: zstd -dcq namemycity.weather.zst | head -n $(expr 3600 \* $(date -u +%H) \+ 60 \* $(date -u +%M) \+ $(date -u +%S)) | tail -n 1

What Mean Column?

Separated By ";" The Column Mean :::: Temperature;Sun;Rain;Snow;Storm;Fog;Wind With Some Condition See My Script In Comment
